<section id="experience">

    <h2>Work Experience</h2>

    <div class="timeline">

        <article class="timemark">

            <header>
                <h3>Full Stack .NET Developer</h3>
                <span>Atlas Proyectos Informáticos</span>
            </header>

            <p>
                <time datetime="2026-03">March 2026</time> - Current
            </p>

            <p>
                I'm currently working as a Full Stack .NET Developer at
                <strong>Atlas Proyectos Informáticos</strong>, where I contribute as an external developer
                for <strong>Atlas Copco</strong>. In this role, I'm involved in the development of
                <strong>Blazor Hybrid</strong> applications, focused on delivering modern, maintainable
                and high-performance enterprise solutions.
            </p>

        </article>

        <article class="timemark">

            <header>
                <h3>Full Stack .NET Developer</h3>
                <span>Memorándum Multimedia</span>
            </header>

            <p>
                <time datetime="2023-10">October 2023</time> -
                <time datetime="2026-03">March 2026</time>
            </p>

            <p>
                Development and maintenance of enterprise web applications using
                <strong>.NET</strong>, <strong>Blazor</strong>, <strong>SQL Server</strong> and <strong>Oracle SQL</strong>,
                working for different public administration and financial-sector clients.
            </p>

            <p>
                My work includes both the creation of new features and the evolution of existing
                internal systems related to processes such as admissions, institutional management,
                accounting workflows and academic tracking systems.
            </p>

            <p>
                I've also been involved in building solutions such as platforms for managing
                collective investment fund documentation, sports entity management systems, and
                corporate objective tracking tools, always focusing on clean architecture,
                maintainability and scalability.
            </p>

        </article>

        <article class="timemark">

            <header>
                <h3>Web Development Intern (Erasmus+)</h3>
                <span>Continero</span>
            </header>

            <p>
                <time datetime="2023-04">April 2023</time> -
                <time datetime="2023-07">July 2023</time>
            </p>

            <p>
                Internship in Brno (Czech Republic) as part of the Erasmus+ programme,
                where I developed a complete web dashboard using <strong>ASP.NET Blazor</strong>
                and <strong>SQL Server</strong>.
                This experience helped me strengthen my backend skills and gain confidence
                working in an international environment.
            </p>

        </article>

    </div>

</section>

@code {

    [Inject]
    public NavigationManager NavigationManager { get; set; } = default!;

    private void Navigate(string page)
    {
        NavigationManager.NavigateTo($"/{page}");
    }

}